refentry.refsect1:
 &reftitle.parameters;


  
    
  link_identifier

The CUBRID connection. If the link identifier is not specified, the last link opened by cubrid_connect is assumed.

  &reftitle.returnvalues;


   An array with CUBRID database parameters; on success.
  


    &false; on failure.

  &reftitle.examples;
  
   cubrid_get_db_parameter example
   

<?php
    $link = cubrid_connect("localhost", 30000, "demodb2", "dba", "");
    if (!$link)
    {
        die('Could not connect.');
    }
    echo "CUBRID parameters:<br>";
    print_r(cubrid_get_db_parameter($link));
?>

   
    &example.outputs;
    

Result:
CUBRID parameters:
Array ( [PARAM_ISOLATION_LEVEL] => 3 [LOCK_TIMEOUT] => -1 [MAX_STRING_LENGTH] => 1073741823 )
